Scripture Floating Quote

But the fruit of the Spirit is
love, joy, peace, patience,
kindness, goodness,
faithfulness, gentleness,
self-control; against such
things there is no law.

Galatians 5:22-23

  • All Floating Quotes are printed on clear acrylic using durable UV ink. The printed portion of the artwork is visible and the rest is see-through.

  • Available with either a clear table-top stand (no frame) or framed in an elegant black or white frame.

  • All frames include a sawtooth hanger installed for easy hanging.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
